To All,<br><br>
We came here to resolve questions about NAM from all points of view.  As this site matures, and it assuredly has, other subjects close to the warrior's heart will rise to the surface.<br><br>
We all are proud of our country and ask a great deal of our Commander and Chief.  In NAM if we could not respect our leader and his judgement we could not follow.  I believe this is where we are now.<br><br>
A country that does not question the strength of its leadership is destined to be lost in the confusion.<br><br>
There is no way that men of our conviction can separate the two. If we are silent we are quilty of complicity.<br>

